title: Eagles - Hell Freezes Over - DTS ONLY - Full DVD -blueschile
description:
The Eagles Hell Freezes over is probably one of the best live concerts available. This version is the full DVD with the video brought down to 65% to make room for the DTS audio track including the Seven Bridges track.

Video - NTSC - 4:3

No Stereo track included. This DVD will have no sound if you dont have a DTS decoder.

Cheers and enjoy,

blusechile
